{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, analyzing the revenue trends across different time periods can help the company to better understand the demand for EV charging services and plan accordingly.",
    "Energy usage for AC charging stations is forecasted in Fig. 19a using the SARIMA model for the last 2 months for already existing data and Fig.",
    "19b uses SARIMA model for future consumption prediction of the AC charging station dataset for 1 month.",
    "EV charging stations that use AC (alternating current) are often used, and they take a lot of energy.",
    "Several variables, such as the charging rate, battery size, and charging duration, have an impact on how much energy AC charging stations use."
  ]
}